    {
      "text": "Skate or Die 2: The Search for Double Trouble is a skateboarding themed action/adventure video game for the Nintendo Entertainment System. The game is a sequel to Skate or Die!.\nThe skater seen on the cover art is Jef Whitehead, who would years later become known for being the sole member of the black metal project Leviathan.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    },
    {
      "text": "Skate or Die 2: The Search for Double Trouble è un videogioco di skateboarding del 1990 sviluppato e pubblicato da Electronic Arts per Nintendo Entertainment System. Il gioco è un seguito di Skate or Die!.",
      "lang": "it",
      "source": "wikipedia_it"
    },
    {
      "text": "Skate or Die 2: The Search for Double Troubleは、任天堂のファミコン用スケートボードをテーマにしたアクションアドベンチャービデオゲームです。本作は『Skate or Die!』の続編にあたります。\nカバーアートに描かれているスケーターはジェフ・ホワイトヘッドで、彼は後にブラックメタルプロジェクト「レヴィアタン」の唯一のメンバーとして知られることになります。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "ai_local_gemma4",
      "base_lang": "en"
    }
